The paper discusses machine learning algorithms for failure prediction in industrial systems, which falls under the category of "Machine Learning" (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of distributed learning, which falls under the categories of "Artificial Intelligence" (cs.AI) and "Systems and Control" (cs.SY). The paper proposes a new algorithm that optimizes the use of computational and communication resources, which falls under the category of "Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing" (cs.DC). Finally, the paper discusses the use of active learning and federated learning, which falls under the category of "Neural and Evolutionary Computing" (cs.NE).
